RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

94-97. State v. Jackson.

Hamilton County, No. C-920430. Reported at 68 Ohio St.3d 1479, 629 N.E,2d 455. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s motion for reconsideration under S.Ct.Prac.R. XI(1)(B). Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective September 29, 1994.
